### REST Client Testing File
### Install REST Client extension in VS Code to use this file
### atau gunakan Postman/Thunder Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Check Server Status
GET http://localhost:3000

###

### 2. Get All Grades
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades

###

### 3. Get All Grades with Filter - by Student
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades?studentID=1

###

### 4. Get All Grades with Filter - by Course
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades?courseID=2

###

### 5. Get All Grades with Filter - by Teacher
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades?teacherID=3

###

### 6. Get All Grades with Multiple Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades?studentID=1&courseID=2

###

### 7. Get Grade by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades/1

###

### 8. Get Grades by Student ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades/student/1

###

### 9. Get Grades by Course ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades/course/2

###

### 10. Get Grades by Teacher ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/grades/teacher/3

###

### 11. Create New Grade - Full Data
POST {{baseUrl}}/grades
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "studentID": 1,
  "courseID": 2,
  "teacherID": 3,
  "grade": "A",
  "remarks": "Excellent work, keep it up!"
}

###

